  James Wan\, Toby Emmerich\, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid\, and executive 
 produced by Michael Clear\, Judson Scott\, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff. <
 br/><br/>Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Ste
 phen F. Windon\, production designer Yohei Taneda\, editor Stuart Levy and
  costume designer Cappi Ireland\, with casting by Rich Delia and music by 
 Benjamin Wallfisch. <br/><br/>New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/B
 roken Road Production\, a Fireside Films Production\, Mortal Kombat II. Th
 e film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures\, only in Au
 stralian cinemas 23 October 2025. <br/>
